# Eventing rules

## EventBridge (outbound)
- Dispatchers in `src/driven/eventbridge/`. Base: `base/event-bridge-dispatcher.ts`.
- Detail types: `od-pdp.<event-name>` (e.g. `od-pdp.enrollment-updated`).
- Payloads: backward-compatible by default. Add fields only; avoid removing/renaming.
- Version payload if breaking (e.g. `detailVersion: 2`).

## SQS consumers (inbound)
- Consumers in `src/driving/nest/sqs/`. Extend `SqsConsumer`, implement `messageHandler`.
- DTOs in `src/driving/nest/sqs/dto/`. Use `parseAndValidate` (Zod/class-validator).
- Retry-safe: design for at-least-once. Consider idempotency keys.
- No PII in logs. Log `messageId`, not payload content.

## Event payloads
- Prefer additive changes. Document breaking changes and version.
